CustomField.description: Override the end date of Project Task using this field. If this date is before the calculated end the calculated end will still be used
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The earliest possible date that this Project Task can finish. The Project Task can still finish after this date but not before. (You might select a value here where you want task to span a week even though there is only 1 days work involved).
CustomField.label: Cannot End Before
